***Solution - I (Using Recursion, Accepted)-***
* The most basic thing we can think of is, we use recursion to solve our question.
* We repeatdly add our number until it lies in the range `0 to 9`.
* See more explanation in the code also.
```
Time Complexity --> O(n) // where n is the length of number, more precisly how many digits it contains
Space Complexity --> O(1) // we don't use anything extra from our side
It paases [ 1101 / 1101] in built test cases
