# Intuition
I wanted to find a basic pattern in this question. So, I just wrote down test cases uptil 50, and noticed that a pattern existed. Also, I checked for some random large numbers.

# Approach
If the number is 0, then just return 0. Else, first calculate the remainder that you will get when you divide the number with 9. If the remainder equals 0, then return 9, else return the remainder itself.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(1)

- Space complexity:
O(1)

